messages.messageBody:
Hello Laura,

I've noticed that you have been looking to come to FL lately. You'd be
more than welcome to spend some time hanging out w/ us.
I just wish we could find unschoolers around here to get together with on
a regular basis. I have a lot of hmschl "friends", but they are not
flexible. It takes a major ordeal to get together. Most of the time they
don't even answer there phone. And when I leave a message, it takes about a
week for a return call. It's very frustrating.
Well, if any of you comes across someone near Daytona... tell them about
us.

Love, Laura

messages.subject: Need fellowship
messages.msgSnippet: Hello.  My name is Laura and I have been reading these posts for a while now. I have just recently started unschooling my two girls. We are in need of some
messages.messageBody:
Hello. My name is Laura and I have been reading these posts for a while now.
I have just recently started unschooling my two girls.

We are in need of some friends to do "field trips" and just general fun "hanging out" kind of stuff. Not to say that the list isn't fun to read.... but it isn't the same as meeting in person.

We live in the Daytona Beach, FL area. If there is anyone out there... we'd be pleased to meet you.

Thanks a million. Laura
